Jason Lewis (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jason_Lewis_(actor) 0 Jason Lewis (born June 25, 1971) is an American actor and former fashion model. He is known for his role as Jerry "Smith" Jerrod on the HBO series Sex and the City. Jason_Lewis ( born June_25_,_1971 ) is an_American_actor and former_fashion_model .
